# Accessible, Secure Enhancements for Property Detail Page

The property details page displays listing info and calls-to-action, so we must ensure **keyboard accessibility**, **clear focus indication**, and **secure scripting**. Currently there is no “skip link”, so adding one (WCAG 2.4.1) will help screen-reader and keyboard users【1†L19-L27】. All interactive elements (buttons, links) need visible focus outlines (WCAG 2.4.7)【3†L31-L39】 and meet 24×24 CSS px size requirements【8†L142-L149】. We use JavaScript DOM methods (`textContent`, `createElement`) for content insertion, avoiding unsafe innerHTML. Key fixes: **P0:** add skip-link and focus styles, ensure contrast ≥4.5:1 for text【6†L68-L72】, label any images (`aria-label` or `alt`). **P1:** make sure the “Share” and “Interested” buttons announce status (e.g. `role="status"` on toast), and any opened links use `noopener`. **P2:** validate query ID and handle missing data gracefully. All suggestions follow W3C and OWASP recommendations【1†L19-L27】【3†L31-L39】【6†L68-L72】.

## Prioritized Changes (P0/P1/P2)

| Priority | Change / Feature                 | Rationale & Standards                                                           | Effort |
|:--------:|:---------------------------------|:-------------------------------------------------------------------------------|:------:|
| **P0**   | **Skip-to-content link**         | Add a hidden “Skip to main” link as first focus item【1†L19-L27】 to bypass nav.  | Med    |
| **P0**   | **Focus indicator**              | Ensure all links/buttons have a clear CSS focus outline (2px)【3†L31-L39】.      | Med    |
| **P0**   | **Contrast ≥4.5:1**             | Text and UI (price, headings) must meet WCAG contrast ratio【6†L68-L72】.         | Med    |
| **P0**   | **Target size ≥24×24 px**        | Buttons/links (e.g. “Share”) should be ≥24×24 CSS px【8†L142-L149】 for touch.    | Low    |
| **P0**   | **Image labels**                 | Hero image has `aria-label`. Thumbnails should have alt/labels if images.        | Low    |
| **P1**   | **ARIA for toast/status**        | Add `role="status"` to toast div so screen readers announce share action.       | Low    |
| **P1**   | **Secure link/window**           | If any link opens a new tab (e.g. property share), use `rel="noopener"`【turn2search3†L0-L3】.| Low |
| **P1**   | **Empty-state handling**         | If ID is invalid, show message (currently redirects). Consider friendly text.    | Low    |
| **P2**   | **Form Semantics**               | Labels for any future inputs; use input attributes (`type="tel"`, `autocomplete`) if adding phone fields. | Low    |
| **P2**   | **Performance (optional)**       | Lazy-load images in gallery; compress assets. Not critical for MVP static data.  | Low    |

*Thresholds:* We maintain WCAG Level AA (4.5:1 contrast)【6†L68-L72】 and large tap targets (24px)【8†L142-L149】. Focus outlines ensure keyboard users see navigation.

