## Deployment Checklist & Sources

- **Content Security & HTTPS:** Serve over HTTPS with HSTS. Enforce CSP via headers (avoid inline JS/style in production)【turn3search3†L0-L3】.
- **Image Accessibility:** Ensure any real `<img>` tags have `alt` text. Decorative images should have empty `alt` or `aria-hidden`.
- **Error Handling:** Validate inputs server-side if integrated (current code assumes trusted IDs). Prevent injection by encoding parameters (we used `encodeURIComponent` for links).
- **Form Autocomplete:** If adding any user input (e.g. phone in future), use `autocomplete` and `inputmode`.
- **Security:** Rate-limit any share/share or back-end endpoints, sanitize all inputs【turn2search10†L0-L3】.
- **Privacy:** No sensitive data collected here. Show only approved listing details, as per user consent models.

